name: MIND HARVEST
description:
After "Siliwangi 3035" released on Tezos blockchain while ago, this track is the next collection from Studio Kuantum.

While Xin Lie explores drumkit of Dog-dog, theres a lot of drafts saved on his drive and "MIND HARVEST" was one of dusty draft stored in Xin Lie's altar then he finally wiped the dust out, then this track can be stored on blockchain.

MIND HARVEST was recorded, mixed, and mastered by Diannov Pamungkas at XLNS, 2021.

Artwork by Interceptor Protocol

KTM002
Studio Kuantum
